                <title>void linearLeak (void *neuron, tw_stime now)</title> <emphasis>A linear leak function.</emphasis>
                
<para>LinearLeak is the standard linear leak function from the paper. Using the leakRate parameter inside <link linkend="struct_neuron_model">the neuron state </link>, this follows a simple linear function, reducing the membrane potential by a fixed rate per tick.</para>

